<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jạynlk rby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - jạynlk rby wbnrfʿ ʿnynạ llsmạʾ wbnṭlb ạlhnạ wbnṭlb fạdynạ

[V2]
 wbnṭlb mnk rḥmẗ wạlmḥbẗ ạlly lynạ yạlly wḥdk sạmʿnạ wbḥbk fạdynạ

[V3]
 1- yạlly wḥdk frḥtnạ tʿạly bạlrwḥ wsṭynạ yạlly fyk tʿzytnạ tʿạly bạlrwḥ ʿzynạ

[V4]
 mḥtạjynlk yạlly dạymạaⁿ btklmnạ mḥtạjynlk yạlly dạymạaⁿ btfrḥnạ

[V5]
 ạnt ạrfʿnạ fwq ạlʿạlm nʿysẖ ạlyk

[V6]
 2- yạlly bdmạk ḥbytnạ tʿạly bsẖfạʾ ḥqyqy ṣạrkẖyn mn kl qlwbnạ tʿạly bslạm ḥqyqy

[V7]
 mḥtạjynlk yạlly qṭʿt qywdnạ mḥtạjynlk yạlly bạlnʿmẗ ạtbnytnạ

[V8]
 wtʿlynạ fwq ạlʿạlm wfwq ạlḍyq

[V9]
 3- yạlly nwrk qdạmnạ wʿạysẖyn lạlh ḥqyqy wfy mlkwtk mkạnạ wbʿhd ạbdy ḥqyqy

[V10]
 mḥtạjynlk yạlly ṣlybk nwr ḥrrnạ mḥtạjynlk yạlly slạmk byrfʿnạ

[V11]
 wlmjdk ʿạysẖyn fy ạlʿạlm wạn mtnạ lyk</lyrics>
<author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<hymn_number>10370</hymn_number>
</song>